The mention of "dominant" strategies and assumptions about future behavior suggests a connection to game theory and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The focus on constructing a system implementation from a specification suggests a connection to software engineering (cs.SE) and programming languages (cs.PL). Finally, the use of compositionality and incremental synthesis suggests a connection to algorithms and data structures (cs.DS).
